To add input fields for manually entering coordinates and customer demands to the GUI, we can update the HTML to include these fields between the vehicle capacity and coordinates elements. We'll also update the JavaScript to handle these new input fields.

### Updated [`VeRyPy-GUI/verypy/gui/index.html`](VeRyPy-GUI/verypy/gui/index.html )

Add input fields for manually entering coordinates and customer demands:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VeRyPy VRP Solver</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>VeRyPy VRP Solver</h1>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>Problem Input</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="vrp-file">Upload .vrp file</label>
                        <input type="file" id="vrp-file" accept=".vrp">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="capacity">Vehicle Capacity</label>
                        <input type="number" id="capacity" placeholder="Enter vehicle capacity">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="manual-coordinates">Manual Coordinates</label>
                        <textarea id="manual-coordinates" rows="5" placeholder="Enter coordinates (one per line, format: index x y)"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="manual-customer-demands">Manual Customer Demands</label>
                        <textarea id="manual-customer-demands" rows="5" placeholder="Enter customer demands (one per line, format: index demand)"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="coordinates">Coordinates</label>
                        <textarea id="coordinates" rows="5" readonly></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="customer-demands">Customer Demands</label>
                        <textarea id="customer-demands" rows="5" readonly></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="algorithm">Select Algorithm</label>
                        <select id="algorithm">
                            <option value="">Choose an algorithm</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <button id="solve">Solve VRP</button>
                    <button id="reset">Reset</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2>Statistics</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <div class="statistics-grid">
                            <div>
                                <h3>Total Distance</h3>
                                <p>1234.5 km</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Total Time</h3>
                                <p>45.6 hours</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Vehicle Utilization</h3>
                                <p>87.5%</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Computation Time</h3>
                                <p>2.3 seconds</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2>Visualization</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <div class="visualization">
                            <div>
                                <div></div>
                                <div></div>
                                <div>Visualization Area</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="playback-controls">
                            <button id="playback">Play</button>
                            <span>Stage: <span id="current-stage">0</span> / 10</span>
                        </div>
                        <input type="range" id="stage-slider" min="0" max="10" value="0">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```

